<h2>Hi {{name}},</h2>

<p>We received a request to reset the password for your EyeWear account.</p>

<p>Click the button below to create a new password:</p>

<p style="text-align: center;">
  <a href="{{resetUrl}}" class="btn">Reset Password</a>
</p>

<p><strong>Or copy and paste this link into your browser:</strong></p>
<p style="word-break: break-all; color: #1976d2;">{{resetUrl}}</p>

<div class="divider"></div>

<div class="info-box">
  <p><strong>Important:</strong></p>
  <ul style="margin: 10px 0; padding-left: 20px; color: #1565c0;">
    <li>This link will expire in 1 hour for your security</li>
    <li>If you didn't request a password reset, please ignore this email</li>
    <li>Your existing password will remain unchanged until you click the link above</li>
  </ul>
</div>

<p>If you have any questions or need assistance, feel free to contact our support team.</p>

<p>Take care,<br>The EyeWear Team</p>
